Code preview of the table CON_优惠信息主表

drop table "CON_MainDiscount" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_MainDiscount" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_MainDiscount"
(
"MainDiscountID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"DiscounttCode" VARCHAR2(30) not null,
"ContractID" NUMBER(32),
BCID NUMBER(32),
"CompanyID" NUMBER(32),
"CompanyCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"EntityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"EntityCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"MallID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"DiscountAmount" NUMBER(10,2) not null,
"DiscountStatusID" INTEGER not null,
"Remark" NVARCHAR2(500),
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_MAINDISCOUNT primary key ("MainDiscountID")
);

comment on column "CON_MainDiscount"."ContractID" is
'包含变更重签合同';

comment on column "CON_MainDiscount"."DiscountStatusID" is
'10：创建未提交
20：提交待批准
30. 审批通过
40. 通过未使用
41：提交待财务审批
50. 已变更使用到合同
';

comment on column "CON_MainDiscount"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0：无效';
